ECB’s Weidmann Says Greece’s Adjustment is ‘Multi-Year Process’

-- B y   R a i n e r   B u e r g i n
-- 
2011-09-26T17:59:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/ecb-s-weidmann-says-greece-s-adjustment-is-multi-year-process-.html
European Central Bank Governing
Council member said the consolidation of  Greece ’s public
finances is a “multi-year process.”  At the same time one shouldn’t always only focus on Greece,
Weidmann said in a panel discussion in  Washington  today. For
instance, “Ireland’s adjustment program works very well,” he
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
